      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·節南山之什·002.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">正月.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>瞻彼阪田，有菀其特。天之扤我，如不我克。
彼求我則，如不我得。執我仇仇，亦不我力。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Look at the rugged and stony field;—
Luxuriantly
rises in it the springing grain.
(But) Heaven moves and shakes me,
As if it could not overcome me.
​They sought me (at first) to be a pattern (to them),
(Eagerly) as if they could not get me;
(Now) they regard me with great animosity,
And will not use my strength.</seg>
      </tuv>
